{"id":237597,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/07/维权网-北京丰台区石榴庄周杰等家凌晨遭遇强拆/","date":"2012-07-04T10:01:32Z","modified":"2012-07-04T10:01:32Z","title":"维权网 | 北京丰台区石榴庄周杰等家凌晨遭遇强拆（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"><span></span><br /><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a><span>（维权网信息员张成报道）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>日</span><span>凌晨，北京丰台区石榴庄来了数百人，把周杰家门砸开，没有任何合法手续，没有征地许可，没有拆迁许可，没有法院判决，周杰家几十万的财物被抢走，房子遭强拆，周杰母亲被打伤。报警三个小时警察不来。</span><span> </span><br /><span>数百黑衣保安还包围其他村民家，截至</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>点钟，包括周杰家在內共有</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>户被强拆。周杰房頂的三面五星红旗也没能保住祖辈的房产。在拆迁现场的右边角落特地来了两辆救护车，可见是精心策划好的。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span><span> </span></p>\n<p><span>同日早上，北京市丰台区双庙村有几百穿黑衣人和穿制服人员将道路封锁，不让通行，有可能将进行强拆。黑衣人将拆迁访民吴丽红手机抢走，吴丽红高呼抢劫，无人理睬。吴丽红走出两里地找电话报警，但超过一小时不见出警。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span><span> </span></p>\n<p><span>周杰联系电话：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">18611207588</span><span> </span><br /><span>相关参见</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">http://wqw2010.blogspot.com/2012/05/blog-post_4645.html</span></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-8bZNUFzFrKM/T_O-VYGsz6I/AAAAAAAAI74/kqXlhm4RD6c/s1600/1.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-8bZNUFzFrKM/T_O-VYGsz6I/AAAAAAAAI74/kqXlhm4RD6c/s320/1.jpg\" width=\"263\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-b7UmlSrouS4/T_O-YBFCENI/AAAAAAAAI8A/WFjhfGcI1TM/s1600/2.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"219\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-b7UmlSrouS4/T_O-YBFCENI/AAAAAAAAI8A/WFjhfGcI1TM/s320/2.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-qvlj_r_X5LM/T_O-Z_MeXkI/AAAAAAAAI8I/0hoK2DrGbQU/s1600/3.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"218\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-qvlj_r_X5LM/T_O-Z_MeXkI/AAAAAAAAI8I/0hoK2DrGbQU/s320/3.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<h3> 